-- German Parliament’s Lower House Approves ESM Euro-Bailout Fund
-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 2012-06-29T19:40:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/german-parliament-s-lower-house-approves-esm-euro-bailout-fund.html
Germany ’s lower house of parliament
approved the euro-area’s permanent bailout fund, the European
Stability Mechanism. The measure won a two-thirds majority in
the chamber, the Bundestag, with 493 lawmakers voting in favor
and 106 voting against.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
